arStrings.szText:
For the next {c_number}20{/c} minutes:
{icon:bullet} Increases Potion Capacity by {c_number}+3{/c} and Healing Received by {c_number}+10%{/c} for all Nearby players.
{icon:bullet} Increases Experience by {c_number}5%{/c}.
This is a type II incense. Only one Incense of a type may be active at a time. Experience Bonus does not stack with other Incenses.
